summary: An Ordinance authorizing the Mayor and City Comptroller to issue Local Improvement Bonds for the improvement of Maple Leaf Avenue Place from Fifth Avenue N.E. to Sixth Avenue N.E. et al in the City of Seattle, by grading under Ordinance No. 20440, creating Local Improvement District No. 2035 prescribing the rate of interest thereon and authorizing their delivery to the contractor constructing the improvement.
